## 🔑 Key Features

### Root Configuration Files
Các file cấu hình ở root level quản lý toàn bộ monorepo:

- **package.json**: 
  - Workspace manager
  - Shared dependencies
  - Root-level scripts
  - PNPM workspace configuration

- **pnpm-workspace.yaml**: 
  - PNPM workspace configuration
  - Defines workspace packages
  - Enables package linking

- **tsconfig.base.json**: 
  - Base TypeScript configuration
  - Shared compiler options
  - Path aliases (@shared, @gateway, etc.)
  - Extended by all packages

- **turbo.json**: 
  - Turborepo configuration
  - Build pipeline
  - Caching strategy
  - Task dependencies

- **docker-compose.yml**: 
  - Infrastructure services
  - PostgreSQL (per service)
  - Redis (cache & Event Bus)
  - MeiliSearch (search)

### Documentation & Scripts

- **docs/**: 
  - Architecture documentation
  - Port management guide
  - Logging guide
  - Structure documentation (`.cursor/rules/structure/`)

- **scripts/**: 
  - `start-all.ps1`: Start all services in development
  - `check-services.ps1`: Health check all services
  - `fix-ports.ts`: Resolve port conflicts

- **logs/**: 
  - Service logs directory
  - Organized by service name

### Packages Structure
Thư mục `packages/` chứa tất cả services và applications:

- **1-gateway/**: API Gateway (BFF Layer) - Port 3000
- **2-services/**: 10 microservices - Ports 3001-3010
- **3-web/**: Next.js Web Frontend - Port 3000 (dev)
- **4-desktop/**: Electron Desktop App
- **5-mobile-ios/**: iOS Native App
- **6-mobile-android/**: Android Native App
- **7-shared/**: Shared Library (no port, imported by all)

